Workman brings archaeological finds in a wheelbarrow from the Digsite to the Varrock Museum for examination.

He cannot be interacted with in any way, and will disappear shortly after emptying his wheelbarrow near the archaeologists.

Dialogue[edit | edit source]

This article on an NPC has an associated dialogue page.
Click here for a transcript of possible conversations with this NPC.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • The Workman is one of the only NPCs (excluding some that only appear in cutscenes) capable of moving at a running speed, due to having a fixed path.
  • There is an unused variant of the Workman who cannot presently be seen anywhere ingame.
